Class GraphicData

java.lang.Object
  testbed.gui.gmi.GraphicData

public class GraphicData
extends java.lang.Object

This class maintains one timestep's worth of data needed to populate a SystemDataPanel.

Constructor Detail

GraphicData

public GraphicData(int _timestep,
                   java.util.Hashtable _bankBalances,
                   java.util.Hashtable _clients,
                   java.util.Hashtable _messageCounts)
Creates a new instance of SystemData from all required data.

Parameters:
_timestep - Timestep during which data is collected.
_bankBalances - A Hashtable, keyed by agent name, of agent bank balances during this timestep.
_appErrAvgs - A Hashtable, keyed by agent name, of agent appraisal error averages during this timestep.
_appErrStDevs - A Hashtable, keyed by agent name, of agent appraisal error standard deviations during this timestep.
_opTransactions - A Hashtable, keyed by agent name, of Hashtables. Inner Hashtables contain a "To" key and "From" key for each other agent in the system. Each element contains the number of opinions sent "To" or "From" the other agent in this timestep.
_repTransactions - A Hashtable, keyed by agent name, of Hashtables. Inner Hashtables contain a "To" key and "From" key for each other agent in the system. Each element contains the number of reputations sent "To" or "From" the other agent in this timestep.
_systemMessages - A Vector of all Messages between all pairs of agents in this timestep.
